prompts.prompt: Create a simple calculator application in Python. The application should be able to perform basic arithmetic operations like addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division. The user should be able to input two numbers and then select the operation to perform. The application should display the result of the operation.

Create a web page with three images centered on the page. Implement a hover effect such that when the mouse cursor moves over any of the images, a tooltip-like box appears displaying a general description of the image. Ensure the layout is responsive and visually appealing.
